// 芒聰聙芒聰聙 Volatility Watchdog + Telegram message 芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙
const raw    = $("Fetch 1M Ticker").first().json;
const result = raw && raw.result ? raw.result : {};
const key    = Object.keys(result)[0];
const ticker = result[key] || {};
const price  = ticker.c ? parseFloat(ticker.c[0]) : 0;
if (!price) {
  return [{ json: { triggered: false, reason: 'No price data', price: 0, ts: new Date().toISOString(), telegramMsg: '' } }];
}

// Kraken ticker: index [0]=today, [1]=24h rolling
const high24    = ticker.h ? parseFloat(ticker.h[1]) : price;
const low24     = ticker.l ? parseFloat(ticker.l[1]) : price;
const open24    = ticker.o ? parseFloat(ticker.o[1]) : price;
const vwap24    = ticker.p ? parseFloat(ticker.p[1]) : price;
const highToday = ticker.h ? parseFloat(ticker.h[0]) : price;
const lowToday  = ticker.l ? parseFloat(ticker.l[0]) : price;

const range24pct = open24 > 0 ? ((high24 - low24) / open24) * 100 : 0;
const rangeToday = open24 > 0 ? ((highToday - lowToday) / open24) * 100 : 0;
const vwapDev    = vwap24 > 0 ? ((price - vwap24) / vwap24) * 100 : 0;
const vwapDevAbs = Math.abs(vwapDev);
const priceMove  = open24 > 0 ? Math.abs((price - open24) / open24) * 100 : 0;
const rangePos   = (high24 > low24) ? (price - low24) / (high24 - low24) : 0.5;
const atExtreme  = rangePos > 0.95 || rangePos < 0.05;

const RANGE_SPIKE_PCT = 6.0;
const PRICE_MOVE_PCT  = 3.0;
const VWAP_DEV_PCT    = 2.0;

const rangeSpike   = range24pct > RANGE_SPIKE_PCT;
const priceSpike   = priceMove  > PRICE_MOVE_PCT;
const vwapSpike    = vwapDevAbs > VWAP_DEV_PCT;
const breakoutSpike = atExtreme && rangeToday > 2.0;

const triggered = rangeSpike || priceSpike || vwapSpike || breakoutSpike;

const reason = [];
if (rangeSpike)    reason.push('24H range ' + range24pct.toFixed(2) + '% > ' + RANGE_SPIKE_PCT + '%');
if (priceSpike)    reason.push('Price move ' + priceMove.toFixed(2) + '% from open');
if (vwapSpike)     reason.push('VWAP dev ' + vwapDevAbs.toFixed(2) + '% (' + (vwapDev > 0 ? 'above' : 'below') + ')');
if (breakoutSpike) reason.push('Range extreme (' + (rangePos * 100).toFixed(0) + '%) + intraday ' + rangeToday.toFixed(2) + '%');

const ts = new Date().toISOString();

// 芒聰聙芒聰聙 Build Telegram Message (only sent when triggered=true) 芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙芒聰聙
const HR = '\u2501'.repeat(20);
const spikeType  = rangeSpike || priceSpike ? 'HIGH' : 'MODERATE';
const spikeEmoji = spikeType === 'HIGH' ? '\uD83D\uDEA8\uD83D\uDEA8' : '\u26A1\u26A1';
const priceDir   = price > open24 ? '\uD83D\uDE80 ABOVE open' : '\uD83D\uDD3B BELOW open';
const vwapDir    = vwapDev > 0 ? '\uD83D\uDFE2 above VWAP' : '\uD83D\uDD34 below VWAP';
const extremeLabel = rangePos > 0.95 ? '\uD83D\uDFE2 near day HIGH \u2014 breakout zone' : rangePos < 0.05 ? '\uD83D\uDD34 near day LOW \u2014 breakdown zone' : '\uD83D\uDFE1 mid-range';

const telegramMsg = [
  spikeEmoji + ' <b>VOLATILITY SPIKE DETECTED</b> ' + spikeEmoji,
  '\uD83D\uDDD3 ' + ts.replace('T', ' ').slice(0, 19) + ' UTC',
  '',
  HR,
  '\uD83D\uDCB0 BTC/USD: <b>$' + Math.round(price).toLocaleString('en-US') + '</b>  \u00B7  ' + priceDir,
  '\uD83D\uDCC8 24H Range: <b>' + range24pct.toFixed(2) + '%</b>' + (rangeSpike ? ' \u26A0\uFE0F SPIKE' : ''),
  '\uD83D\uDCD0 Intraday Range: <b>' + rangeToday.toFixed(2) + '%</b>',
  '\uD83C\uDFAF VWAP Dev: <b>' + (vwapDev >= 0 ? '+' : '') + vwapDev.toFixed(2) + '%</b>  \u00B7  ' + vwapDir,
  '\uD83D\uDCCD Range Position: <b>' + (rangePos * 100).toFixed(0) + '%</b>  \u00B7  ' + extremeLabel,
  '',
  HR,
  '\uD83D\uDD0D <b>Trigger reasons:</b>',
  reason.map(r => '\u2022 ' + r).join('\n') || '\u2022 Composite spike score',
  '',
  '\uD83D\uDD04 <b>Action:</b> Extra analysis scan triggered outside 5-min schedule',
  '',
  '<i>\u23F1 Normal schedule resumes in 5 min  \u00B7  v3-super</i>'
].join('\n');

return [{ json: {
  triggered,
  price,
  range24pct:  Math.round(range24pct  * 100) / 100,
  rangeToday:  Math.round(rangeToday  * 100) / 100,
  priceMove:   Math.round(priceMove   * 100) / 100,
  vwapDev:     Math.round(vwapDev     * 100) / 100,
  rangePos:    Math.round(rangePos    * 100) / 100,
  atExtreme,
  reason: reason.join(' | ') || 'normal vol',
  ts,
  telegramMsg: triggered ? telegramMsg : ''
}}];
